title: The Paper (short student movie)
description: This is a short movie I made in college. The budget was around $60, so I guess it didn&#039;t turn out too badly! It&#039;s about five years old at this point, and was shot on SVHS (pre-MiniDV), so it isn&#039;t the best quality. Anyway, enjoy it for what it&#039;s worth. It&#039;s not like you paid for it! ;) And best of all, I promise not to sue you for downloading it!
